{"pageid":347880,"pagename":"Ghost (Hopespear)","title":"Ghost (Hopespear)","displaytitle":"Ghost (Hopespear)","revid":14273631,"redirects":["Hopespear","Hope spear"],"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Ghost_(Hopespear).png"},{"name":"description","value":"Hopespear (known simply as ghost in-game) is the name of an ancient goblin prophet who fought alongside the Narogoshuun tribe at the Battle of Plain of Mud in the Fourth Age. During the battle, in which eleven out of the twelve Goblin Tribes (exception being the Dorgeshuun) fought, Hopespear had a vision of the Big High War God and gathered the leaders of the warring goblin tribes, telling them to stop the battle as their god would one day send a Chosen Commander to lead the goblins to victory."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile navigation-not-searchable rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Ghost (Hopespear).\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Ghost_(Hopespear)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Ghost (Hopespear)\">rsw:Ghost (Hopespear)</a></span></div>\n<table class=\"infobox infobox-npc\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-header\">Ghost</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content\"><a href=\"/w/File:Ghost_(Hopespear).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Ghost (Hopespear).png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Ghost_%28Hopespear%29.png/170px-Ghost_%28Hopespear%29.png?2d158\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"170\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Ghost_%28Hopespear%29.png/255px-Ghost_%28Hopespear%29.png?2d158 1.5x, /images/thumb/Ghost_%28Hopespear%29.png/340px-Ghost_%28Hopespear%29.png?2d158 2x\" data-file-width=\"902\" data-file-height=\"1369\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\">Released</th><td colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/w/9_February\" title=\"9 February\">9 February</a> <a href=\"/w/2022\" title=\"2022\">2022</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Land_of_the_Goblins\" title=\"Update:Land of the Goblins\">Update</a>)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a></th><td colspan=\"12\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Races\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Races\">Race</a></th><td colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/w/Goblin\" title=\"Goblin\">Goblin</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Locations\" title=\"Locations\">Location</a></th><td colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/w/Goblin_Cave\" title=\"Goblin Cave\">Goblin Cave</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Quest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Quest\">Quest</a></th><td colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/w/Hopespear%27s_Will\" title=\"Hopespear&#39;s Will\">Hopespear's Will</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Choose_Option\" title=\"Choose Option\">Options</a></th><td colspan=\"12\">Talk-to</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Examine\" title=\"Examine\">Examine</a></th><td colspan=\"12\">A ghostly goblin warrior.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Map</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content infobox-image\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Ghost_(Hopespear)?action=edit\"><b>?</b> (edit)</a></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"8\">NPC ID</th><td colspan=\"12\">11301</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Ghost_(Hopespear)_chathead.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Ghost (Hopespear) chathead.png\" src=\"/images/Ghost_%28Hopespear%29_chathead.png?a3cf8\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"78\" height=\"98\" data-file-width=\"78\" data-file-height=\"98\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>Hopespear</b> (known simply as <b>ghost</b> in-game) is the name of an ancient <a href=\"/w/Goblin\" title=\"Goblin\">goblin</a> prophet who fought alongside the <a href=\"/w/Narogoshuun\" title=\"Narogoshuun\">Narogoshuun</a> tribe at the <a href=\"/w/Battle_of_Plain_of_Mud\" title=\"Battle of Plain of Mud\">Battle of Plain of Mud</a> in the <a href=\"/w/Fourth_Age\" title=\"Fourth Age\">Fourth Age</a>. During the battle, in which eleven out of the twelve Goblin Tribes (exception being the <a href=\"/w/Dorgeshuun\" title=\"Dorgeshuun\">Dorgeshuun</a>) fought, Hopespear had a vision of the <a href=\"/w/Big_High_War_God\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Big High War God\">Big High War God</a> and gathered the leaders of the warring goblin tribes, telling them to stop the battle as their god would one day send a <a href=\"/w/Zanik\" title=\"Zanik\">Chosen Commander</a> to lead the goblins to victory.\n</p><p>Hopespear currently resides in the <a href=\"/w/Goblin_Temple\" title=\"Goblin Temple\">Goblin Temple</a> crypt, only visible to players wearing a <a href=\"/w/Ring_of_visibility\" title=\"Ring of visibility\">ring of visibility</a>. He can only be spoken to with the aid of a <a href=\"/w/Ghostspeak_amulet\" title=\"Ghostspeak amulet\">ghostspeak amulet</a>. After the <a href=\"/w/Quest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Quest\">quest</a> <a href=\"/w/Land_of_the_Goblins\" title=\"Land of the Goblins\">Land of the Goblins</a>, players can start the <a href=\"/w/Hopespear%27s_Will\" title=\"Hopespear&#39;s Will\">Hopespear's Will</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/Miniquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Miniquest\">miniquest</a> if they meet the requirements.&#160;\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Ghost_(Hopespear)?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Ghost_(Hopespear)?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Hopespear is very similar in appearance to his original <i><a href=\"/w/RuneScape_2\" title=\"RuneScape 2\">RuneScape 2</a></i> model, with some minor differences in his facial features.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Hopespear&#39;s Will\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Hopespear%27s_Will\" title=\"Template:Hopespear&#39;s Will\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Hopespear%27s_Will\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Hopespear%27s_Will?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Hopespear%27s_Will\" title=\"Hopespear&#39;s Will\">Hopespear's Will</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">NPCs</td><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-parent\" style=\"padding:0\"><table class=\"na