in Temple</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Yu%27biusk\" title=\"Yu&#39;biusk\">Yu'biusk</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Transcript:Hopespear%27s_Will\" title=\"Transcript:Hopespear&#39;s Will\">Transcript</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐gcmxr\nCached time: 20220516215316\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.091 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.133 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 306/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 19099/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 656/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.031/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1069569/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   80.803      1 -total\n 55.10%   44.523      1 Template:Infobox_NPC\n 26.67%   21.550      1 Template:Hopespear's_Will\n 23.71%   19.161      2 Template:Navbox\n 17.69%   14.297      1 Template:External\n  5.58%    4.513      1 Template:Ctg\n  2.67%    2.159      6 Template:Chatl\n  2.63%    2.126      5 Template:Plink\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:347880-0!canonical and timestamp 20220516215316 and revision id 14273631. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs}}\n{{Infobox NPC\n|name = Ghost\n|image = [[File:Ghost (Hopespear).png|170px]]\n|release = [[9 February]] [[2022]]\n|update = Land of the Goblins\n|members = Yes\n|race = [[Goblin]]\n|quest = [[Hopespear's Will]]\n|location = [[Goblin Cave]]\n|options = Talk-to\n|examine = A ghostly goblin warrior.\n|map = \n|id = 11301\n}}\n[[File:Ghost (Hopespear) chathead.png|left]]\n'''Hopespear''' (known simply as '''ghost''' in-game) is the name of an ancient [[goblin]] prophet who fought alongside the [[Narogoshuun]] tribe at the [[Battle of Plain of Mud]] in the [[Fourth Age]]. During the battle, in which eleven out of the twelve Goblin Tribes (exception being the [[Dorgeshuun]]) fought, Hopespear had a vision of the [[Big High War God]] and gathered the leaders of the warring goblin tribes, telling them to stop the battle as their god would one day send a [[Zanik|Chosen Commander]] to lead the goblins to victory.\n\nHopespear currently resides in the [[Goblin Temple]] crypt, only visible to players wearing a [[ring of visibility]]. He can only be spoken to with the aid of a [[ghostspeak amulet]]. After the [[quest]] [[Land of the Goblins]], players can start the [[Hopespear's Will]] [[miniquest]] if they meet the requirements. \n\n==Trivia==\n* Hopespear is very similar in appearance to his original ''[[RuneScape 2]]'' model, with some minor differences in his facial features. \n\n{{Hopespear's Will}}\n[[Category:Goblins]]\n[[Category:Bandosians]]"}